was through
a professional answering service.

192
00:08:44,774 --> 00:08:46,822
SARAH: Everyone told her
she was crazy at the time.

193
00:08:46,985 --> 00:08:48,505
- Right?
- DEBORAH: They certainly did.

194
00:08:48,528 --> 00:08:50,030
