You chose to.

203
00:09:10,341 --> 00:09:12,343
Well, I did or they wouldn't
have stayed with me.

204
00:09:12,510 --> 00:09:13,887
- True.
- I wouldn't have had a business.

205
00:09:14,054 --> 00:09:15,601
You know.

206
00:09:18,183 --> 00:09:20,857
MIA: <i>As the days pass,
